Name and Identity

The faith is formally known as Hjöskjöldrism

Also referred to as:
The Hjöskjöldrian Faith
The Reformed Church of Hjöskjöldrism

Hjöskjöldrism is a mystic Christian-derived spiritual philosophy centered on ascension, protection, and moral strength.

The name is derived from Hjöskjöldr, a philosophical concept representing the balance of sword and shield. Action and protection, strength and mercy.
